对了，我指的是存档地图名字的颜色和武器名字和介绍，还有伤害，这些怎么改？ ...
存档颜色就用NBTEdit
武器名字和介绍的颜色/斜体之类就用那个黑科技
武器名字和介绍的NBT：{display:{Name:"名字",Lore:["第一行","第二行"]}}
例子：give @a diamond_sword 1 0 {display:{Name:"名字",Lore:["第一行","第二行","第三行"]}}

伤害：（增加一个固定的数目）
{AttributeModifiers:[{AttributeName:"generic.attackDamage",Name:"attack Damage",Amount:增加数值,Operation:0,UUIDLeast:1,UUIDMost:1}]}

比如
/give @a minecraft:diamond_sword 1 0 {AttributeModifiers:[{AttributeName:"generic.attackDamage",Name:"attack Damage",Amount:50,Operation:0,UUIDLeast:1,UUIDMost:1}]}
就是增加50点伤害

伤害：（乘一个固定的数目）
{AttributeModifiers:[{AttributeName:"generic.attackDamage",Name:"attack Damage",Amount:倍数,Operation:1,UUIDLeast:1,UUIDMost:1}]}

比如
/give @a minecraft:diamond_sword 1 0 {AttributeModifiers:[{AttributeName:"generic.attackDamage",Name:"attack Damage",Amount:50,Operation:1,UUIDLeast:1,UUIDMost:1}]}
就是50倍
